==English==

===Noun===

{{en-noun|s}}
A mashing together of "feminist" and "robot": a woman who mindlessly believes and repeats the lies, distortions, misperceptions, half-truths, and bogus claims routinely heard in Feminist Studies classes, and who typically reacts with stunned shock (often combined with indignation bordering on anger) when her illusions are debunked or refuted with logic and fact - like a robot being fed discordant data.

